# Competency question: "What language-proficiency levels does GMEOW model, and on
# which scales?" Expected: the ProficiencyLevel value individuals — the CEFR band
# (A1–C2) plus scale-free native/heritage — each tied to its scale by
# gmeow:levelScale. The leveled detail lives on the reified gmeow:LanguageProficiency.

PREFIX gmeow: <https://blackcatinformatics.ca/gmeow/>

SELECT ?level WHERE {
    ?level a gmeow:ProficiencyLevel .
}
ORDER BY ?level
